                <h1 class="account-header account-header-low-margin-top">Monthly to Yearly: The Billing Period Change</h1>
                
                                    <p class="hidden-xs">
                        Course:
                        <a class="knp-color-black" href="resume"><em>Stripe Level 2: Subscriptions, Discounts, Webhooks, oh my! Tutorial</em></a>                    </p>
