<p>Now, if <code>$plan</code> - which is the new plan - <code>$plan-&gt;getDuration()</code> matches the
<code>$currentUserPlan-&gt;getDuration()</code>, then we <em>should</em> correct the total. Otherwise,
if the duration is changing, the <code>$total</code> is already perfect:</p>
