        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>That's the current period start date <em>before</em> we change the plan.</p>
<p>After we change the plan, if the duration is different, the current period start
will have changed. Surround the <em>entire</em> invoicing block with if
<code>$stripeSubscription-&gt;current_period_start == $currentPeriodStart</code>:</p>
